name: Private Gulfstream G650ER [N650VC] Landing and Taxi at Calgary Airport ᴴᴰ
description:
What a fantastic looking aircraft! I've never been quite lucky enough to film Gulfstream's flagship aircraft, the G650ER in action, but I happened to be out spotting already when this fairly new G650 arrived, after a round trip two hour flight around Alberta. Not quite sure what it was doing or why it was here, but I'm glad to have filmed it! Gonna have to look out for these more often, Gulfstream makes some fantastic looking bizjets. ATC is included, enjoy my first catch of a G650ER!

Thanks for watching!
